p: Cluster III: β-phellandrene and β-bisabolene. MHP and RHP were classified into this cluster. They were pericarps of HLW. They contained more β-phellandrene, a relative percentage of 26.13% and 23.15%, respectively. Percentages of β-bisabolene and cis-α-santalol were also relatively large (6.59–10.21%).
